  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK928">
<l>kaḷittaṟiyē ṉeṉpatu kaiviṭuka neñcat </l>
<l>toḷittatūu māṅkē mikum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (the drunkard) give up saying "I have never drunk"; (for) the moment (he drinks) he will simply betray his former attempt to conceal.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
